---
title: "❓ Help"
labels: ["help", "question"]
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        # ❓ Need Help?

        Got a question or need assistance? Please provide:
        Our community and maintainers are here to help you get the most out of {{ image.name }}.

  - type: textarea
    id: question
    attributes:
      label: Your Question
      description: What would you like help with?
      placeholder: "Please describe your question or the issue you're encountering"
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: context
    attributes:
      label: Context
      description: Provide more context about your situation
      placeholder: "What were you trying to do? What's your use case?"

  - type: textarea
    id: steps-taken
    attributes:
      label: Steps You've Already Tried
      description: What have you already tried to solve this?
      placeholder: |
        - I tried...
        - I checked...
        - I read...

  - type: textarea
    id: environment
    attributes:
      label: Environment
      description: Share relevant environment details
      value: |
        - OS: [macOS/Linux/Windows]
        - {{ image.name }} version: [e.g., 1.0.0]
        - Docker version: [e.g., 24.0]

  - type: textarea
    id: error-output
    attributes:
      label: Error Messages or Output
      description: If applicable, share any error messages or relevant output
      render: bash
      placeholder: |
        Paste error output or logs here...

  - type: textarea
    id: additional-info
    attributes:
      label: Additional Information
      description: Any other details that might help?
      placeholder: "Code snippets, configuration files, screenshots, etc."
